location.fullValue: Julian Plan, The Springs at Skyline Trails

data.description: Nestled in the heart of Yukon this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is the epitome of modern comfort and style. With a spacious open floor plan and a wealth of desirable amenities, this residence is sure to capture your heart. As you step inside, you'll be immediately struck by the sense of space and openness that defines this home. The living area seamlessly flows into the kitchen, making it the perfect spot for entertaining friends and family. The kitchen boasts a large island with seating, perfect for casual meals or hosting gatherings. Prepare your favorite meals with ease on ample countertops and top-of-the-line appliances, all while enjoying the company of your loved ones. Both bathrooms are adorned with beautiful tiled showers, and one of them even features a relaxing tub for those moments of well-deserved self-care. This home offers practicality as well as elegance. A spacious laundry room simplifies your daily routines, while a cute mud bench helps keep you organized and clutter-free. Step outside, and you'll discover two covered porches – one in the front and one in the backyard. These outdoor spaces provide the ideal setting for sipping your morning coffee or watching the sunset in the evenings. The backyard is fully privacy-fenced, ensuring that you can enjoy your outdoor oasis in peace and seclusion. Plus, the property backs up to a nature-filled private property, offering a tranquil backdrop for your outdoor adventures. Located in the highly sought-after Mustang School District. Don't miss your opportunity to own this Yukon gem only 5 minutes away from popular shopping including Target, Crest, HomeGoods, and more! Schedule a viewing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and privacy in this beautiful home.
